{"tid":176403,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"健明邨雙程證少婦上吊　家姑揭發救回","createTime":"2017-03-28T07:19:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-28T13:20:23.000Z","uid":122,"like":1,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9b38056cac2772862053adb5b0c27eaff2837a7c","tid":176403,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T07:19:36.000Z","msg":"健明邨雙程證少婦上吊　家姑揭發救回<br />\n<br />\n將軍澳健明邨女子家中自縊獲救，中午12時20分，一名持雙程證由內地來港會夫的少婦（20餘歲），在明宇樓寓所上吊，其家姑剛巧帶同兩名幼童買餸回家揭發，立即報警求助，救護員到場將昏迷少婦送院搶救，警方正展開調查。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n防止自殺求助熱線： <br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會：2389 2222 <br />\n生命熱線：2382 0000 <br />\n明愛向晴軒：18288 <br />\n社會福利署：2343 2255 <br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)︰28960000"},{"pid":"c2e221cda09ca0597bdcbb00dd4dbdfb4abc51ad","tid":176403,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T07:20:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 未死"},{"pid":"204dcaa0b66cd4f20fec47ff25d3267325877d57","tid":176403,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T07:20:18.000Z","msg":"佢老公幾多歲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"809e425b9ff92ae24447fe7d4a4a62fcc4adf1e1","tid":176403,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T07:21:08.000Z","msg":"咁都唔撚死，下次跳樓丫嗎！"},{"pid":"6a8be22c5672076b2d4472a72b1f592886a8bf2d","tid":176403,"uid":33908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T07:29:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 特快綜援<br />\n識玩手段"},{"pid":"6e51922f71ff3a98556db0afc113120f2a87575b","tid":176403,"uid":997,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T07:29:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁都唔撚死，下次跳樓丫嗎！</blockquote>"},{"pid":"4879f90329fa559d173560716609bb1f4bf22f7d","tid":176403,"uid":25794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T07:30:50.000Z","msg":"連自殺都失敗, 支那西真係廢, 再繼續努力啦"},{"pid":"9aba72d4631f28bae6d1a5a2533bc76433d1